comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-07T09:44:04.849Z",codex-agent,"Integrator story update: pm-6abs adds hermetic package smoke-test diagnostics. A package author can run pm package doctor --project --isolated --detail deep --trace or isolate PM_GLOBAL_PATH for a whole test process; temp-dir dogfood proved a fresh package loaded only project:pm-temp-smoke."
  "2026-07-08T06:06:35.422Z",codex,"Evidence: package-consumer SDK proof now exercises the installed @unbrained/pm-cli SDK from a packed tarball in /tmp, covering init/create/update/claim/release/comments/notes/learnings/files/docs/deps/schema/profile/context/next/health/validate and returning ok with created item pm-yp8p and child pm-gps8."
  "2026-07-16T20:25:24.310Z",codex-wide-sdk-20260716,"Acceptance implementation start 2026-07-16: validate the complete custom-tool story through a real SDK-only exemplar and packed temporary consumer proof."
  "2026-07-16T21:18:33.308Z",codex-wide-sdk-20260716,"Acceptance evidence: the SDK-only exemplar now exercises create, update, claim, release, close, list, search, context, comments, notes, learnings, files, docs, dependencies, schema customization, health, and validate. Both linked SDK suites passed, installed-tarball proof passed in a fresh consumer, and repo-wide coverage is 100/100/100/100."
  "2026-07-16T22:10:15.082Z",codex-wide-sdk-20260716,"Acceptance follow-up: the SDK-only consumer is now directly executable through its declared pm-custom bin and completes the real customization/lifecycle/context/graph/governance scenario with PM_AUTHOR propagation, structured JSON output, clean health, and clean history validation."
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-16T21:18:34.288Z",codex-wide-sdk-20260716,"The universal-tool story is strongest when one coherent consumer crosses customization, lifecycle, context, graph, evidence, and governance boundaries and returns machine-checkable proof rather than isolated API snippets."
